## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on a limited number of sources and may not capture the full spectrum of reasons why individuals break the law. Additionally, the complexity of human behavior means that motivations can vary widely among individuals and contexts. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, would provide a more nuanced understanding of this issue.

